---
---
<section class="wcu" id="why-choose-us">
  <div class="wcu-inner">
    <div class="wcu-header">
      <h2 class="display-headline wcu-headline reveal">
        With So Many Trainers Out There…<br /><em>Why Choose Us?</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="wcu-layout">
      <!-- Left: image -->
      <div class="wcu-image reveal-scale">
        <img src="/sm2.png" alt="Samara Michael" loading="lazy" />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: copy + badges + cta -->
      <div class="wcu-right">
  
        <p class="body-lora wcu-para reveal">
          We have an online Academy called <strong>the Amazon Kickstarter Academy</strong> where we've been teaching Amazon FBA for the past <strong>6 years</strong>.
          It's where we teach people how to correctly run an FBA business while abiding by Amazon's policies,
          how to source from UK-based suppliers only, and the secret formulas to finding the best-selling products.
        </p>

        <p class="body-lora wcu-para reveal">
          Over <strong>1,500 graduates</strong> have achieved their life of financial freedom — quitting their stressful
          9-to-5s, spending more time with their families, and building a halal income stream for themselves
          and their loved ones.
        </p>

        <p class="body-lora wcu-para reveal">
         While this academy was a huge powerhouse in churning 6-Figures FBA Business owners, it was simpley a premium experience which not many folks could afford, that's why we created this bootcamp with budget-crafted in mind to give everyone a shot at building a legit profitable business without risking their budget on courses.
        </p>

    

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wcu-cta reveal">
      <a href="#offer" class="btn-primary">I Want In Now!</a>
      <p class="wcu-urgency">Doors close March 1st — Seats are limited</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .wcu {
    background: var(--color-near-black);
    padding: 130px 0 110px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .wcu::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-gold), transparent);
    opacity: 0.25;
  }

  .wcu-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 60px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .wcu-header {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }

  .wcu-headline {
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 56px);
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .wcu-headline em {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .wcu-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 420px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Left image */
  .wcu-image {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .wcu-image img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  /* Right copy */
  .wcu-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .wcu-sub {
    font-size: 11px !important;
  }

  .wcu-para {
    color: var(--color-beige);
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    line-height: 1.78;
  }

  .wcu-para strong {
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Badges */
  .wcu-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.15);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .wcu-badge {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.1);
    transition: background 0.25s ease;
  }

  .wcu-badge:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .wcu-badge:hover {
    background: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.05);
  }

  .wcu-badge-icon {
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .wcu-badge-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .wcu-badge-desc {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-beige);
    opacity: 0.6;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .wcu-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 64px;
  }

  .wcu-urgency {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #E03030;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .wcu { padding: 72px 0 64px; }
    .wcu-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .wcu-image { position: static; max-width: 340px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .wcu-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
    .wcu-header { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  }
</style>
